<h1> Honors Faculty Recomendation Form </h1>

<p>
	This is a recommendation for an applicant to the Honors Program to be filled out by a faculty member. You have received the invitation to fill out this recommendation because an applicant has requested you to support his/her application. If you have not been contacted by a student regarding his/her application to the Honors Program or if you believe you have received this due to an error, please contact the Associate Director of the Honors Program, Emily Marks (emarks@babson.edu) right away.

This recommendation is due by no later than February 15th, 2012. Please help us by submitting this reference on time. 

All applicants to the Honors Program have at least a 3.3 GPA and so we need your help in making fine distinctions among many well qualified applicants. Your input helps ensure that the most deserving students are accepted into this very competitive program. We greatly value your thoughts and sincerely thank you for your time.
</p>

